original: Kylen, Gert Ivar Emil, tandläkare, Falkenberg, f. 13/4/99 i Falköping av distr:vet. Erik K. o. Hanna Tho-mander. G. 25 m. gymn :dir. Rigmor Strige. Barn: Monika f. 26, Erik 28, Per 32. — Stud:ex. i Skara 18, tandl:-kand. 20, tandläk. 22. Egen praktik i Falkenberg sed. 22, förest, f. skoltand-poiliklin. där 22-30. Hobbies: jakt, schack, bridge.
translated: Kylen, Gert Ivar Emil, dentist, Falkenberg, b. 13/4/99 in Falköping to district veterinarian Erik K. and Hanna Thomander. Married on 25th with gymnastics director Rigmor Strige. Children: Monika b. 26, Erik b. 28, Per b. 32. — High school diploma in Skara in 18, dental student in 20, dentist in 22. Own practice in Falkenberg since 22, supervisor of school dental clinic there from 22-30. Hobbies: hunting, chess, bridge.
